# ARBITRAGE-PRO Data Flow Diagrams

## Complete Data Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[CEX/DEX APIs] --> B[Connector Layer]
    B --> C[Discovery Engine]
    C --> D[Market Data Buffer]
    
    D --> E[Arbitrage Engine]
    E --> F[Opportunity Detector]
    F --> G{Risk Check}
    
    G -->|Low Risk| H[Opportunity Queue]
    G -->|High Risk| I[Discard]
    
    H --> J[Alert Service]
    H --> K[Execution Router]
    
    K --> L{User Tier}
    L -->|Manual| M[Human Review]
    L -->|Simulated| N[Paper Trading]
    L -->|Automated| O[Guardrails Check]
    
    O -->|Pass| P[Trade Execution]
    O -->|Fail| Q[Block + Log]
    
    M --> R{Approve?}
    R -->|Yes| P
    R -->|No| S[Reject]
    
    P --> T[Trade Record]
    T --> U[Audit Log]
    
    J --> U
    Q --> U
    S --> U
```

## Market Data Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Binance WebSocket] --> B[Binance Connector]
    C[Coinbase WebSocket] --> D[Coinbase Connector]
    E[OKX REST API] --> F[OKX Connector]
    G[Uniswap Subgraph] --> H[Uniswap Connector]
    
    B --> I{Parse?}
    D --> I
    F --> I
    H --> I
    
    I -->|Yes| J[Normalize]
    I -->|No| K[Discard]
    
    J --> L{Validate?}
    L -->|No| K
    L -->|Yes| M[Price Snapshot]
    
    M --> N[Redis Cache]
    M --> O[PostgreSQL]
    
    N --> P[WebSocket Broadcast]
    O --> Q[Historical Storage]
    
    P --> R[Web Dashboard]
    P --> S[Mobile App]
```

## Discovery Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start Discovery] --> B[Query Exchange APIs]
    B --> C{Response OK?}
    
    C -->|No| D[Retry with Backoff]
    D --> E{Retries Exhausted?}
    E -->|No| B
    E -->|Yes| F[Mark Exchange Down]
    
    C -->|Yes| G[Parse Trading Pairs]
    G --> H{New Pair?}
    
    H -->|Yes| I[Add to Registry]
    H -->|No| J{Updated Metadata?}
    
    J -->|Yes| K[Update Registry]
    J -->|No| L{Delisted?}
    
    L -->|Yes| M[Remove from Registry]
    L -->|No| N[Keep Existing]
    
    I --> O[Persist to DB]
    K --> O
    M --> O
    N --> O
    
    O --> P[Broadcast Update]
    F --> Q[Alert Ops Team]
```

## Arbitrage Detection Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start Detection] --> B[Fetch Market Snapshots]
    B --> C{Snapshots < 5s old?}
    
    C -->|No| D[Skip Cycle]
    C -->|Yes| E[Group by Pair]
    
    E --> F{Multiple Exchanges?}
    F -->|No| G[Skip Pair]
    F -->|Yes| H[Compare Prices]
    
    H --> I{Spread > Threshold?}
    I -->|No| G
    I -->|Yes| J[Calculate Fees]
    
    J --> K[Calculate Net Profit]
    K --> L{Profitable after fees?}
    
    L -->|No| G
    L -->|Yes| M[Check Liquidity]
    
    M --> N{Liquidity sufficient?}
    N -->|No| G
    N -->|Yes| O[Score Risk]
    
    O --> P[Calculate Confidence]
    P --> Q[Create Opportunity]
    
    Q --> R[Persist to DB]
    R --> S[Broadcast via WebSocket]
    
    G --> T[End Cycle]
    D --> T
    S --> T
```

## Execution Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User Click Execute] --> B{Authentication Valid?}
    
    B -->|No| C[Redirect to Login]
    B -->|Yes| D{Opportunity Expired?}
    
    D -->|Yes| E[Show Error]
    D -->|No| F{Risk Tier?}
    
    F -->|Manual| G[Create Dry Run]
    F -->|Simulated| H[Run Simulation]
    F -->|Automated| I[Check Guardrails]
    
    I --> J{All Pass?}
    J -->|No| K[Log Block]
    J -->|Yes| L[Execute Buy Order]
    
    L --> M{Buy Filled?}
    M -->|No| N[Retry/Cancel]
    M -->|Yes| O[Execute Sell Order]
    
    O --> P{Sell Filled?}
    P -->|No| Q[Retry/Cancel]
    P -->|Yes| R[Calculate P&L]
    
    R --> S[Record Trade]
    S --> T[Update Stats]
    T --> U[Send Notification]
    
    G --> V[Show Review UI]
    H --> W[Show Results]
    K --> X[Show Block Reason]
    N --> Y[Show Error]
    Q --> Y
    
    V --> Z[Await User Action]
    Z --> AA{User Approves?}
    AA -->|Yes| L
    AA -->|No| AB[Discard]
```

## Risk Scoring Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Opportunity] --> B[Liquidity Score]
    A --> C[Volatility Score]
    A --> D[Exchange Score]
    A --> E[Bridge Score]
    A --> F[MEV Risk Score]
    A --> G[Network Score]
    
    B --> H{Weighted Average}
    C --> H
    D --> H
    E --> H
    F --> H
    G --> H
    
    H --> I{Score > 50?}
    
    I -->|No| J[High Risk Flag]
    I -->|Yes| K[Medium Risk Flag]
    
    J --> L[Block Automated]
    K --> M[Allow with Caution]
    
    L --> N[Log Decision]
    M --> N
```

## Alert Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Opportunity Detected] --> B[Load Alert Rules]
    B --> C{User Has Rules?}
    
    C -->|No| D[Skip]
    C -->|Yes| E[Match Against Rules]
    
    E --> F{Any Match?}
    F -->|No| D
    F -->|Yes| G[Check Cooldown]
    
    G --> H{Cooldown Active?}
    H -->|Yes| D
    H -->|No| I[Build Notification]
    
    I --> J[Push via Expo]
    I --> K[Send Email]
    I --> L[Send SMS]
    
    J --> M[Log Alert]
    K --> M
    L --> M
    
    M --> N[Update Last Triggered]
    N --> D
```

## WebSocket Message Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Detector Worker] --> B{Publish?}
    B -->|Yes| C[WebSocket Gateway]
    
    C --> D{Subscribers?}
    D -->|No| E[Drop]
    D -->|Yes| F[Broadcast]
    
    F --> G[Client A]
    F --> H[Client B]
    F --> I[Client C]
    
    G --> J[Update UI]
    H --> J
    I --> J
    
    J --> K[Play Sound]
    J --> L[Show Toast]
    J --> M[Vibrate]
```

## Cache Invalidation Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Price Update] --> B[Write to Redis]
    B --> C[Write to PostgreSQL]
    
    C --> D{Related Cached?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Invalidate Cache]
    D -->|No| F[Keep Cache]
    
    E --> G[Delete Key]
    G --> H{Subscribers?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Notify Subscribers]
    H -->|No| J[End]
    
    F --> J
    I --> J
```

## Error Handling Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[API Request] --> B{Valid?}
    
    B -->|No| C[400 Bad Request]
    B -->|Yes| D{Authenticated?}
    
    D -->|No| E[401 Unauthorized]
    D -->|Yes| F{Authorized?}
    
    F -->|No| G[403 Forbidden]
    F -->|Yes| H{Found?}
    
    H -->|No| I[404 Not Found]
    H -->|Yes| J{Valid Data?}
    
    J -->|No| K[422 Validation Error]
    J -->|Yes| L[Process Request]
    
    L --> M{Success?}
    M -->|No| N[500 Server Error]
    M -->|Yes| O[200/201 Success]
    
    C --> P[Error Log]
    E --> P
    G --> P
    I --> P
    K --> P
    N --> P
    
    P --> Q[Alert if Critical]
    O --> R[Success Log]
```

## Rate Limiting Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Incoming Request] --> B{Authenticated?}
    
    B -->|No| C[Anonymous Limit]
    B -->|Yes| D{User Tier?}
    
    D -->|Free| E[Free Limit]
    D -->|Premium| F[Premium Limit]
    D -->|Admin| G[Admin Limit]
    
    C --> H{Under Limit?}
    E --> H
    F --> H
    G --> H
    
    H -->|Yes| I[Allow Request]
    H -->|No| J[429 Too Many Requests]
    
    I --> K[Increment Counter]
    K --> L[Update Headers]
    
    L --> M[Process Request]
    J --> N[Return Retry-After]
```

## Database Transaction Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start Transaction] --> B[Acquire Connection]
    B --> C[Set Isolation Level]
    
    C --> D{Operation Type?}
    
    D -->|Read| E[SELECT Query]
    D -->|Write| F[INSERT/UPDATE]
    
    E --> G{Result OK?}
    F --> H{Constraints Pass?}
    
    G -->|No| I[Rollback]
    H -->|No| I
    
    G -->|Yes| J[Continue]
    H -->|Yes| J
    
    J --> K{More Operations?}
    K -->|Yes| D
    K -->|No| L[Commit]
    
    L --> M[Release Connection]
    I --> M
    
    M --> N{Error?}
    N -->|Yes| O[Log + Alert]
    N -->|No| P[Return Result]
```

## Health Check Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Health Check Request] --> B{Liveness or Readiness?}
    
    B -->|Liveness| C[Check Process]
    B -->|Readiness| D[Check Dependencies]
    
    C --> E{Process Healthy?}
    E -->|No| F[503 Unhealthy]
    E -->|Yes| G[200 Healthy]
    
    D --> H[Check Database]
    D --> I[Check Redis]
    D --> J[Check Connectors]
    
    H --> K{DB OK?}
    I --> L{Redis OK?}
    J --> M{Connectors OK?}
    
    K -->|No| N[503 Degraded]
    L -->|No| N
    M -->|No| N
    
    K -->|Yes| O[Continue]
    L -->|Yes| O
    M -->|Yes| O
    
    O --> P{All OK?}
    P -->|Yes| G
    P -->|No| N
    
    F --> Q[End]
    G --> Q
    N --> Q